<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <title>Sukuu Activation Email</title>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="styles.css"> <!-- Link to the external CSS file -->
</head>

<body>
  <div class="email-wrapper">
    <div class="email-header">
      <h1>Welcome to <span class="sukuu-learning">Sukuu Learning</span></h1>
    </div>
    <div class="email-body">
      <h1>Hi <span class="user-name">
          <%= user.name %>
        </span>,</h1>
      <p>Thanks for signing up for Sukuu Learning! We're excited to have you as an early user.</p>
      <p>Before we get started, we just need to confirm that this is you. Use this activation code:</p>
      <h2 class="activation-code">
        <%= activationCode %>
      </h2>
      <p>Please enter this code on the activation page. The code will expire in 5 minutes.</p>
      <p>If you didn't sign up for Sukuu, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
      <p>Thanks,<br />The Sukuu Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="email-footer">
      <p>You received this email because you signed up for Sukuu. If you didn't sign up, you can safely ignore this
        email.</p>
      <p>Â© 2023 Sukuu, Inc. All rights reserved. Sukuu is a registered trademark of Sukuu, Inc.</p>
      <p>If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact us at <a
          href='mailto:support@sukuu.com'>support@sukuu.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>